png','Incantation that channels the power of the Dragonkin Soldiers. Creates a spear of ice lightning and stabs it into the ground from above. On impact, the spear will burst into trails of lightning advancing forwards. The Dragonkin were born in the Eternal City, where they knew no true sky, nor true lightning. Instead, ice lightning was their weapon.','Stabs with ice lightning spear from above','Frozen Lightning Spear',NULL,1,'Incantations',36),(341,'/images/incantations/incantation_341.png','One of the incantations of Dragon Communion.','Channels dragon to spew icy breath.','Glintstone Breath',NULL,1,'Incantations',36),(342,'/images/incantations/incantation_342.png','An incantation of Erdtree Worship.','Greatly increases lightning resistance for self and allies','Golden Lightning Fortification',NULL,1,'Incantations',30),(343,'/images/incantations/incantation_343.png','Incantations originating from the maddening Three Fingers.','Emits concentrated blast of yellow flame of frenzy from eyes','Frenzied Burst',NULL,1,'Incantations',24),(344,'/images/incantations/incantation_344.png','One of the incantations that draws directly from the power of the','Hurls massive ball of raging fire','Giantsflame Take Thee',NULL,2,'Incantations',32),(345,'/images/incantations/incantation_345.png','An incantation of Erdtree Worship.','Increases attack and defense for self and allies','Golden Vow (spell)',NULL,1,'Incantations',47),(346,'/images/incantations/incantation_346.png','Superior incantation taught by Gurranq, the Beast Clergyman. ','Creates beast claws to rend surroundings with shockwaves','Gurrang\'s Beast Claw',NULL,1,'Incantations',21),(347,'/images/incantations/incantation_347.png','One of the incantations of the Golden Order fundamentalists. ','Increases left-hand shield\'s affinity/ailment resistance','Immutable Shield',NULL,1,'Incantations',15),(348,'/images/incantations/incantation_348.png','Incantation of the Two Fingers\' faithful.','Heals HP for you and nearby allie