INSERT INTO `npcs` VALUES (1,'/images/NPCs/npcs_1.png',NULL,NULL,'Limgrave, Church of Elleh','Merchant Kalé',NULL),(2,'/images/NPCs/npcs_2.png',NULL,NULL,'Limgrave, Waypoint Ruins','Sorceress Sellen',NULL),(3,'/images/NPCs/npcs_3.png',NULL,'I\'m a prisoner, and these are my chains. I\'m trapped by the Hold, undying, smithing for you fools. That\'s all there is to it.','Roundtable Hold','Smithing Master Hewg',NULL),(4,'/images/NPCs/npcs_4.png',NULL,'Everyone who came with me. They crossed the sea for me. They fought, for me. Heh... Only to have their arms taken. Their legs taken. Even their heads...taken. Taken and stuck to the spider. ','Stormhill Shack, Roundtable Hold','Roderika',NULL),(5,'/images/NPCs/npcs_5.png',NULL,'For a small donation, I\'d be happy to share my knowledge.','Church of Irith in Liurnia of the Lakes','Thops',NULL),(6,'/images/NPCs/npcs_6.png',NULL,'The Fingers guide us all. And you Tarnished, you are here to take, are you not?','Roundtable Hold','Enia',NULL),(7,'/images/NPCs/npcs_7.png',NULL,'I Welcome you, to the Church of Vows. I am Miriel, steward of this sacred chamber. My apologies, for the unseemly state of affairs. Do you know the origin of this place?','Church of Vows','Miriel, Pastor Of Vows',NULL),(8,'/images/NPCs/npcs_8.png',NULL,'Well, look at you. We don\'t receive many visitors','Kingsrealm Ruins, Western Liurnia of the Lakes','War Counselor Iji',NULL),(9,'/images/NPCs/npcs_9.png',NULL,'The pleasure\'s mine. Rogier\'s the name. A sorcerer, as you might have guessed.','Stormveil Castle','Sorcerer Rogier',NULL),(10,'/images/NPCs/npcs_10.png',NULL,'I feel it\'s stench on you... death. Feed it to me.','Bestial Sanctum, Caelid','Gurranq, Beast Clergyman',NULL),(11,'/images/NPCs/npcs_11.png',NULL,'Hm? Oh, yes I remember. Some clod turned me into a tree.','Limgrave','Boc The Seamster',NULL),(12,'/images/NPCs/npcs_12.png',NULL,'I teach incantations, the strength granted us by the Two Fingers, and explore the secrets of the Golden Order. So that one day, if a Tarnished of the Roundtable Hold should become Elden Lord, I might counsel them, ensuring order regains its proper form, righting rule over men.','Roundtable Hold','Brother Corhyn',NULL),(13,'/images/NPCs/npcs_13.png',NULL,'Insert NPC quote here.','Roundtable Hold','D, Hunter Of The Dead',NULL),(14,'/images/NPCs/npcs_14.png',NULL,'Let me ask you something Are you here in the Lands Between to take up the fight? Does your faith in the guidance of grace hold firm, despite the collapse of the Golden Order?','Warmaster\'s Shack, Volcano Manor','Knight Bernahl',NULL),(15,'/images/NPCs/npcs_15.png',NULL,'But please, can you offer poor ill-starred Pidia...','Caria Manor','Pidia, Carian Servant',NULL),(16,'/images/NPCs/npcs_16.png',NULL,NULL,'Mohgwyn Dynasty Mausoleum','Imprisoned Merchant',NULL),(17,'/images/NPCs/npcs_17.png',NULL,'Have you heard of the finger maidens? They serve the Two Fingers, offering guidance, and aid, to the Tarnished. But you, I am afraid, are maidenless. I can play the role of maiden.','The beginning of the Tarnished\'s journey.','Melina',NULL),(18,'/images/NPCs/npcs_18.png',NULL,'Be on your way. Perhaps we will meet again, if fate permits','Limgrave: near Seaside Ruins','Bloody Finger Hunter Yura',NULL),(19,'/images/NPCs/npcs_19.png',NULL,'I am Alexander, also known as the Iron Fist. And as you can see, I\'m stuck here.','Kevin Howarth','Iron Fist Alexander',NULL),(20,'/images/NPCs/npcs_20.png',NULL,'Are you familiar with grace? The golden light that gives life to you Tarnished You may also behold its golden rays pointing in a particular direction at times That is the guidance of grace. The path that a Tarnished must travel.','Various Locations','White-faced Varré',NULL),(21,'/images/NPCs/npcs_21.png',NULL,'Unless thou should take the crown?\"','Limgrave','Renna',NULL),(22,'/images/NPCs/npcs_22.png',NULL,'Great champion, would you allow me to hold you, but briefly?','Roundtable Hold','Fia',NULL),(23,'/images/NPCs/npcs_23.png',NULL,'Even if the castle should fall, as commander, I must remain.','Castle Morne, Weeping Peninsula','Edgar',NULL),(24,'/images/NPCs/npcs_24.png',NULL,'My good father secreted me out the castle, but decided himself to stay. He says it\'s his duty, as commander. I... I fear for father\'s life.','Bridge of Sacrifice, Weeping Peninsula','Irina',NULL),(25,'/images/NPCs/npcs_25.png',NULL,'Hello? Is anybody there? Someone who might be interested on rescuing the great Kenneth Haight? Servant of the true Order, and celebrated repudiator of the false!, O Erdtree! Grant me succour!','Limgrave','Kenneth Haight',NULL),(26,'/images/NPCs/npcs_26.png',NULL,'Now, Queen Marika the Eternal is nowhere to be found, and in the Night of the Black Knives Godwyn the Golden was first to perish. Soon, Marika\'s offspring, demigods all, claimed the shards of the Elden Ring. The mad taint of their newfound strength triggered the Shattering.','???','Queen Marika',NULL),(27,'/images/NPCs/npcs_27.png',NULL,'The tale of House Hoslow is told in blood. I, Diallos, swear to deliver that promise.','Roundtable Hold','Knight Diallos',NULL),(28,'/images/NPCs/npcs_28.png',NULL,'All I wanted was to fight. To fight, as a warrior, to the last... So, Why? Why, O guidance of grace, will this door not open?','Northernmost part of Limgrave','Frustrated Spirit',NULL),(29,'/images/NPCs/npcs_29.png',NULL,'...','Roundtable Hold','Twin Maiden Husks',NULL),(30,'/images/NPCs/npcs_30.png',NULL,'All I wanted was to fight. To fight, as a warrior, to the last... So, Why? Why, O guidance of grace, will this door not open?','Northernmost part of Limgrave','Frustrated Spirit',NULL),(31,'/images/NPCs/npcs_31.png',NULL,'As a Tarnished who wishes to stand before the Elden Ring and become Elden Lord, I am accumulating knowledge. To be all-knowing.','Roundtable Hold','Gideon Ofnir',NULL),(32,'/images/NPCs/npcs_32.png',NULL,'I\'m Patches. Patches the Untethered.','Murkwater Cave','Patches',NULL),(33,'/images/NPCs/npcs_33.png',NULL,'Hello? Is someone there? My name is Hyetta, and I\'m journeying in search of the distant light. If I might be so bold as to ask... would you donate any Shabriri grapes in your possession to me? My eyesight has been weak since birth, you see. I can\'t tell which way I\'m supposed to go next.','Various Locations','Hyetta',NULL),(34,'/images/NPCs/npcs_34.png',NULL,'You, please, I can read them. Your fingers, please, your fingers...','Multiple Locations','Palm Reader',NULL),(35,'/images/NPCs/npcs_35.png',NULL,'Be proud. You were a fine warrior. Your only mistake was your choice of master.','Stormveil Castle','Nepheli Loux',NULL),(36,'/images/NPCs/npcs_36.png',NULL,'A pleasure to meet you, Brave Tarnished.','Volcano Manor','Rya',NULL),(37,'/images/NPCs/npcs_37.png',NULL,'I am Tanith, the proprietress of this house. An honour to have you.','Volcano Manor','Tanith',NULL),(38,'/images/NPCs/npcs_38.png',NULL,'I am the witch Ranni. I stole Death long ago, and search now for the dark path.','Ranni\'s Rise, Three Sisters','Ranni The Witch',NULL),(39,'/images/NPCs/npcs_39.png',NULL,NULL,'Stormveil Castle Entrance','Gatekeeper Gostoc',NULL),(40,'/images/NPCs/npcs_40.png',NULL,'A mysterious and silent figure residing near the Hermit Village.','Hermit Village, Mt. Gelmir','Primeval Sorcerer Azur',NULL),(41,'/images/NPCs/npcs_41.png',NULL,'I told you not to disturb me','Roundtable Hold','Dung Eater',NULL),(42,'/images/NPCs/npcs_42.png',NULL,'I don\'t know what it is the mistress sees in a provincial Tarnished like you, but since we have the misfortune of serving the same Lady, I ask that you kindly try not to drag us all down with you.','Seluvis\'s Rise, Three Sisters','Preceptor Seluvis',NULL),(43,'/images/NPCs/npcs_43.png',NULL,'The name\'s Blaidd. I\'m looking for a man who goes by \"Darriwil.\"','Mistwood Ruins','Blaidd',NULL),(44,'/images/NPCs/npcs_44.png',NULL,'The rotting sickness that afflicts Millicent has no cure. When the Erdtree flourished, even the demigods could not stave off its effects, despite their nigh godhood.','Gowry\'s Shack, Caelid','Gowry',NULL),(45,'/images/NPCs/npcs_45.png',NULL,'I would rather trust you than simply continue to spoil from within. ','Church of the Plague','Millicent',NULL),(46,'/images/NPCs/npcs_46.png',NULL,'...I\'ve still my pride. I\'m not going out like a complete monster.','Seaside Ruins, Stormhill , Stormveil Castle','Bloodhunter Raz',NULL),(47,'/images/NPCs/npcs_47.png',NULL,'Foul tarnished, what do you want?','Liurnia of the Lakes, Slumbering Wolf\'s Shack','Latenna',NULL),(48,'/images/NPCs/npcs_48.png',NULL,'Please, no. Dear me!. I haven\'t a clue. No secrets lie with me, not a one.','Village of the Albinaurics, Liurnia of the Lakes','Albus',NULL),(49,'/images/NPCs/npcs_49.png',NULL,NULL,'Roundtable Hold','Ensha Of The Royal Remains',NULL),(50,'/images/NPCs/npcs_50.png',NULL,'May chaos take the world! May chaos take the world!','Mountaintops of the Giants','Shabriri',NULL),(51,'/images/NPCs/npcs_51.png',NULL,'Brave champion, you have our gratitude','Redmane Castle plaza Church','Witch-hunter Jerren',NULL),(52,'/images/NPCs/npcs_52.png',NULL,'.....','Altus Plateau, ','Goldmask',NULL),(53,'/images/NPCs/npcs_53.png',NULL,' Never met someone with a taste for prawns I couldn\'t trust. ','Boilprawn Shack','Blackguard Big Boggart',NULL),(54,'/images/NPCs/npcs_54.png',NULL,'???','Cathedral of, the Forsaken','Three Fingers',NULL),(55,'/images/NPCs/npcs_55.png',NULL,'...','Caelid','The Great-jar',NULL);
