ismans/talismans_21.png','Dragoncrest Shield Talisman',NULL,'Wrought iron talisman depicting a trio of ancient dragons. Boosts physical damage negation.'),(22,'Boosts fire damage negation.','/images/talismans/talismans_22.png','Flamedrake Talisman',NULL,'Talisman depicting a red ancient dragon. Boosts fire damage negation.'),(23,'Raises fire attack, but lowers damage negation','/images/talismans/talismans_23.png','Fire Scorpion Charm',NULL,'A talisman carried by assassins who strike unseen. Patterned on a scorpion freshly shed of its exoskeleton, its claws seizing a heart that burns with fire.'),(24,'Successive attacks restore HP','/images/talismans/talismans_24.png','Godskin Swaddling Cloth',NULL,'Sacred cloth of the Godskin Apostles, made from supple skin sewn together.'),(25,'Raises potency of Incantations','/images/talismans/talismans_25.png','Faithful\'s Canvas Talisman',NULL,'A talisman bearing an icon that depicts a group of masked figures. Raises potency of incantations.'),(26,'Vastly Raises maximum equip load (~19%)','/images/talismans/talismans_26.png','Great-jar\'s Arsenal',NULL,'A charm that resembles a great jar overflowing with weaponry. Vastly boosts maximum equipment load.'),(27,'Boosts holy damage negation.','/images/talismans/talismans_27.png','Haligdrake Talisman',NULL,'Talisman depicting a golden ancient dragon. Boosts holy damage negation.'),(28,'Raises stamina recovery speed.','/images/talismans/talismans_28.png','Green Turtle Talisman',NULL,'A talisman in the shape of a green turtle. Raises stamina recovery speed.'),(29,'Enhances stamina-reducing attacks against blockers.','/images/talismans/talismans_29.png','Hammer Talisman',NULL,'A talisman depicting a hammer and a knight. Enhances stamina-reducing attacks against a blocking opponent.'),(30,'Raises Immunity','/images/talismans/talismans_30.png','Immunizing Horn Charm',NULL,'An accountrement worn by the ancestral followers. Raises immunity. (Immunity governs resistance to poison and rot.)'),